1. create super head then iterate:â€¨   if head.val == val: pre remains pre.next point to head.next else: pre move to head O(n) O(1)

class Solution(object):
    def removeElements(self, head, val):
        superHead = ListNode(-1)
        superHead.next = head
        pre = superHead
        while head != None:
            if head.val == val:
                pre.next = head.next
            else:
                pre = head
            head = head.next
        return superHead.next


1. first time WA: forget to link super head: superHead.next = head
